_:N9e6ea33bce344c7dbf8aee6f5fa3aed2 <http://schema.org/description> "The Boundary Commission for Scotland (BCS) carries out boundary reviews of parliamentary constituencies in Scotland, and submits its recommendations to the government. BCS is an advisory non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Scotland Office ." .
